attributes.action: Dissolve parliment and call a general election
attributes.action_prefix: We the undersigned petition the Prime Minister to
attributes.background: We the people hereby call on the Prime Minister to dissolve Parliment by the 30th June 2009 and call a general election. If by the 30th June 2009 the Prime Minister has not carried out said action. Then with the backing of 2 million signatures of this petition, we the people kindly request that Her Majesty, The Queen dissolve parliment and call an election in the interests of subjects.

reasons: Duplicate - this is similar to and/or overlaps with an existing petition or petitions
